{"tid":1907580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[偽命題]因為前線巴要坐監所以港女唔會嫁比佢哋？","createTime":"2020-03-02T16:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T09:44:45.000Z","uid":130981,"like":59,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"558817a02beb34150163a17bbf835b0ef6ff034d","tid":1907580,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"討論今生只嫁前線巴根本就係多9餘<br />\n<br />\n1.爭取到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span>就可以解決一切問題<br />\n所以點解要堅持到底<br />\n釋放所有被政治檢控嘅手足咪唔會有前線手足要坐監囉<br />\n<br />\n2.爭取唔到 清算嗰陣不用分前中後線 只要你黃 中共遲早都清算到你<br />\n做港豬就叫一時風平浪靜 但到頭來當中共收割你嗰陣你咪又係任人魚肉 根本就殊途同歸 退一世就海闊天空<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇下藏族維族<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第時可能逼你嫁個女比蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.發大黃色經驗圈<br />\n如果多d黃色良心僱主 政治檢控嘅案底根本唔會影響到手足 反而仲係佢英勇嘅象徵 係話比大家知佢為香港付出左幾多 一般嘅案底代表個人犯過錯 而政治檢控嘅案底代表佢為香港付出過 對抗過不義嘅政權 <br />\n<br />\n你嘅歲月靜好 只因有人替你負重前行<br />\n<br />\n真正上得前線嘅 都唔係為左食女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e48f3bb3062f31081e1167ad157144734e0004e","tid":1907580,"uid":130981,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我印象中 歲月靜好好似係蝗語"},{"pid":"80d5f7157fec06ae8f5284045e6e6201b32a5a4e","tid":1907580,"uid":140924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排真係好多奇怪post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666a037bf9f3f33a757b114c6d2fc8aa61ee2623","tid":1907580,"uid":130981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g